SendToModule(AbSession)

Sends the OptionObject to a specific Abatab Module.

Declaration

Parameters
Type Name Description
AbSession abSession

The Abatab session object.
Remarks
  • The module component of the Script Parameter determines what Abatab Module the OptionObject will be sent to.
  • This method ignores all other Script Parameter components, since they will be handled by the recieving module's Roundhouse class.
